'''Foolxumo''' waa heer qofka  astaamaha muuqaalkiisa loo arko inuu yahay mid aan qurxooneen. Shay foolxun waxaa la dhahaa jafaliil.

==Takoorid==
Takoorida ka dhanka ah dadka aan soo jiidashada laheyn ayaa mararka qaar loogu yeeraa cacophobia (sidoo kale aschimophobia),<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Warhurst|first1=Chris |last2=van den Broek|first2=Diane |last3=Hall|first3=Richard |last4=Nickson|first4=Dennis |date=February 2009 |title=Lookism: The New Frontier of Employment Discrimination? |journal=Journal of Industrial Relations |volume=51 |issue=1 |pages=131–136 |doi=10.1177/0022185608096808 |issn=0022-1856}}</ref> iyo hadii ay tahay natiijada qofka oo daciif noqda , [[ableism|awood u leh]].<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Reel |first1=Justine J. |first2=Robert A. |last2=Bucciere |title=Ableism and body image: Conceptualizing how individuals are marginalized |journal=Women in Sport and Physical Activity Journal |volume=19 |issue=1 |year=2010 |pages=91–97|doi=10.1123/wspaj.19.1.91 }}</ref> [[Teratophobia]] waa diidmada ama cabsida dadka umuuqda kuwa bahalnimada leh, cilado ama muuqaal doorsoon. Diidmada noocaas ah ay weheliso takoornimo, waxaa loo arki karaa inay tahay xoog sheegasho.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Steinberg|first1=Neil|title=Facial discrimination: Living with a disfigured face|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/06/23/health/facial-discrimination-disfigured-face/index.html|website=CNN|publisher=[[CNN]]|access-date=30 August 2016}}</ref>
==Sharci==
Waxaa jira awoodo sharci ah oo horeyba sharci darro uga dhigaya in lagu takooro iyadoo lagu saleynayo qaabab qurxan oo muuqaal qurux leh, oo ay ku jirto gobolka Victoria ee Australiya, halkaasoo muuqaalka laga dhigay sharci darro 1995.<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Harris |first1=Candice |first2=Jennie |last2=Small |title=Obesity and hotel staffing: Are hotels guilty of 'lookism'? |journal=Hospitality & Society |volume=3 |issue=2 |year=2013 |pages=111–127 |doi=10.1386/hosp.3.2.111_1}}</ref> Sidoo kale, sida laga soo xigtay The Economist, magaalada  Washington DC ee maraykanka waxay leedahay sharciyo mamnuucaya muuqaalka.<ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://www.economist.com/books-and-arts/2011/08/27/the-line-of-beauty |magazine=The Economist |title=The line of beauty |date=27 August 2011}}</ref>




